  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.4.0-alpha01\" data-text=\"Version 1.4.0-alpha01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.4.0-alpha01</h3>\n<p>November 9, 2022</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.compose.compiler:compiler:1.4.0-alpha01</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/31382b61f1af46fc43d9a781645ca9eed1b56874..a1e318590b217ecfce1b2de17eed2f18b6a680bb/compose/compiler\">Version 1.4.0-alpha01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix ability to return early from inline composable functions (<a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/255350755\">b/255350755</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix bug in decoy lowering which broke Kotlin/JS support in Compose (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/platform/frameworks/support/+/2265412\">6a40f8</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"version_13_2\" data-text=\"Version 1.3\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.3</h2>",
